snippet.title: Finnish Cottage 8 - DEMO Now on Steam
snippet.description:
In this Finnish Cottage, all is not as it seems. No matter how you try to leave, you'll always find yourself back at the cottage, and strange, horrific changes (called "anomalies") may occur. To escape, you must identify whether or not an anomaly has happened 8 times in a row correctly. 

"Finnish Cottage 8" Demo - NOW on Steam (link in profile).

#horrorgame #indiegame #gaming #steamnextfest
